Description: sslurl
        ======
        
        sslurl is a URL HTTP to HTTPS redirection website. If it receives a
        request for a URL starting with "http://", it redirects to the URL with
        "http://" changed to "https://".
        
        setup
        =====
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            pip install sslurl
        
        Flask
        =====
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            while true; do
                sslurl
            done
        
        Gunicorn
        ========
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            gunicorn --workers=2 "sslurl.__init__:WSGI()" --bind=0.0.0.0:80
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
